# Imports & Path Aliases

## Rule: Always Use `@/` Aliases

Never use relative `../` imports. Always use the `@/` alias which maps to `src/`.

```js
// ✅ CORRECT
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/Button'
import { getProducts } from '@/lib/api/products'
import { ROUTES } from '@/config/routes'
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils/cn'
import { products } from '@/lib/data/products'
import { useScrollPosition } from '@/hooks/useScrollPosition'

// ❌ WRONG — fragile, breaks on folder moves
import { Button } from '../../../components/ui/Button'
import { getProducts } from '../../lib/api/products'
```

---

## Alias Map (`jsconfig.json`)

```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "@/*":            ["./src/*"],
      "@/components/*": ["./src/components/*"],
      "@/features/*":   ["./src/features/*"],
      "@/lib/*":        ["./src/lib/*"],
      "@/hooks/*":      ["./src/hooks/*"],
      "@/config/*":     ["./src/config/*"]
    }
  }
}
```

---

## Import Order Convention

Maintain this order in every file (separated by blank lines):

```js
// 1. Next.js built-ins
import Image from 'next/image'
import Link from 'next/link'
import { notFound } from 'next/navigation'

// 2. React
import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'

// 3. Third-party packages
import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form'
import { z } from 'zod'

// 4. Internal — components
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/Button'
import SectionHeader from '@/components/ui/SectionHeader'

// 5. Internal — features
import ProductGrid from '@/features/products/ProductGrid'

// 6. Internal — lib / data / hooks / config
import { getProducts } from '@/lib/api/products'
import { products } from '@/lib/data/products'
import { ROUTES } from '@/config/routes'
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils/cn'
```

---

## Next.js Specific Imports

Always prefer Next.js built-ins over plain HTML/React equivalents:

| Instead of | Use |
|---|---|
| `<img src="..." />` | `<Image src="..." />` from `next/image` |
| `<a href="...">` | `<Link href="...">` from `next/link` |
| `useNavigate()` from react-router | `useRouter()` from `next/navigation` |
| `useParams()` from react-router | `params` prop on `page.jsx` |
| `<Redirect to="..." />` | `redirect()` from `next/navigation` |
